%% Flow I & J — Tip selection and Mollie payment lifecycle
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor G as Guest
    participant App as Guest Web
    participant API as Backend
    participant M as Mollie
    participant W as Webhook Worker
    participant Staff as Staff Console

    G->>App: Review share amount
    App->>G: Tip screen (0/5/10/15/custom)
    Note over App: Distinguish service charge vs optional tip
    G->>App: Confirm tip + Pay
    App->>API: POST checkout.create
    API->>M: Create payment (iDEAL/card)
    M-->>App: Redirect checkout URL
    G->>M: Complete payment

    par Return URL
        M-->>App: Redirect back pending
        App->>API: GET payment status poll
    and Webhook (source of truth)
        M->>W: webhook paid/failed/expired
        W->>API: Idempotent ledger update
    end

    alt paid
        API-->>App: Success + receipt opt-in
        API-->>Staff: Remaining balance updated
        API->>API: loyalty.accrued if linked
    else partial table balance
        API-->>App: Banner €X.XX remaining
        API-->>Staff: Payment monitor alert
    else failed/expired
        API-->>App: Retry payment CTA
    end

    Note over Staff: Close table blocked until remaining ≈ €0
